{"tid":2240112,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"How the political prisoners are being treated in SAR prison?","createTime":"2020-10-12T12:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T13:24:24.000Z","uid":251732,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3c21f043e1ea14ae0437e9688835f2bc291861b8","tid":2240112,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:22:22.000Z","msg":"Original article: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2239871/page/15\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2239871/page/15</a><br />\n[有圖] 大家知唔知道坐緊監既手足遭受緊啲咩既對待？<br />\nAs the civil resistance has gradually cooled, the SAR dictatorship regime also began a large-scale political purging. Because of this, many protesters and political activists were sentenced to &quot;correctional institutions&quot; by pro-CCP judges. MOST OF THEIR AGES ARE BETWEEN 14 TO 24.<br />\nAmong these so-called &quot;correctional institutions,&quot; it advertises three &quot;S&quot; functions of &quot;Short&quot; sentence, strict &quot;Sharp,&quot; and strong deterrence &quot;Shock&quot; to achieve the effect of penalizing the prisoners in a short time.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DW7dnDu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDW7dnDu.gif&h=38dcbf5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>The following scene refers from the movie &quot;With Prisoners&quot; which based on real experience from ex-prisoners<br />\nWARNING: The following content may be disturbing to some viewers </strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6XOgkqH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6XOgkqH.gif&h=334e84fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nUnder strict control inside the correctional camps, all prisoners must receive &quot;disciplinary training.&quot; Every step of daily life, prisoners must apply to the instructor, even applying for admission to the dining hall, it must make sure all food must be in order lists, and no food remains.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vpv20re.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVpv20re.gif&h=cc8dd842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBecause the oppressive system offers instructors with absolute power, they will beat the shit out of the young prisoners when they wanted to satisfy personal desires and superiority by abuse of power.<br />\nThe torture methods are endless suffers for the prisoner and forced to appreciated their &quot;treatment&quot; from the guards.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o7jSDdB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo7jSDdB.gif&h=42706896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAccording to &quot;HKFP,&quot; there were many famous tortures named by young prisoners in their vocabulary. For example, &quot;Chicken wings&quot; being beaten on the back heavily with an elbow while in a bowing position, &quot;Shaved ice&quot; using finger joint grinding rib position, and &quot;Kale&quot; knee hitting on the thighs.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AfpLdNr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAfpLdNr.gif&h=96fdc63a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nUnder this inhumane environment, some prisoners tried to commit suicide because of hopeless situations and physical abuse. Disciple, most of the attending tries will fail as the correctional officers always keep their eyes open. In other words, prisoners in a life of living hell by giving up their dignity to obey the oppressive order inside the camps.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8q1tV1g.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8q1tV1g.gif&h=55981a35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cGva9mh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcGva9mh.jpg&h=0515903a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nEven there was a mechanism of &quot;Justice of the Peace,&quot; just a PR whitewashing as all complaints from prisoners are handled by the CSD (Correctional Services Department) itself, which means there was no independent department like the complaints council. The CSD will also maintain its official attitude to &quot;emphasize&quot; that will conduct an investigation. But in the end, there will be no clear accusation report written by the bureau because most of the prisoners are afraid of an extended sentence if they dare to resist.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T0g2god.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT0g2god.jpg&h=a4ec9516&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVigktX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVigktX.gif&h=e2e73174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OtIjcydLiTI&amp;ab_channel=MovistoryHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOtIjcydLiTI%26ab_channel%3DMovistoryHK&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2VxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=1af01f95\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OtIjcydLiTI&amp;ab_channel=MovistoryHK</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sG0x_q3Rq8I&amp;t=102s&amp;ab_channel=%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97Demosisto\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsG0x_q3Rq8I%26t%3D102s%26ab_channel%3D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597Demosisto&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2VxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=9a8ae9c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sG0x_q3Rq8I&amp;t=102s&amp;ab_channel=%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97Demosisto</a>"},{"pid":"4993014686996fdc52b4bd10e613a40ca22cc812","tid":2240112,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:26:55.000Z","msg":"push 1"},{"pid":"4d0f418b05498c14f627eb620fa5b02eef1776ee","tid":2240112,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:27:05.000Z","msg":"push 2"},{"pid":"ec552ec7526bc01ac5